{{Infobox video game | title = Dark Train: Coupe | image = Dark Train Coupe cover.jpg | developer = [[Paperash Studio]] | publisher = | director = | producer = | designer = | programmer = | artist = | writer = | composer = | engine = [[Unity (game engine)|Unity]] | platforms = [[Microsoft Windows]], [[OS X]] | released = Q1 2018 | genre = [[Visual novel]] | modes = [[Single-player video game|Single-player]] }}
'''Dark Train: Coupe''' is an upcoming [[visual novel]] by [[Paperash Studio]]. It is a prequel to [[Dark Train]]. The game was announced on 16 May 2017.<ref name="Dark Train se vrací se samostatnou textovou adventurou Coupe - Games.cz">{{cite web|title=Dark Train se vrací se samostatnou textovou adventurou Coupe|url=https://games.tiscali.cz/oznameni/dark-train-se-vraci-se-samostatnou-textovou-adventurou-coupe-297436|website=Games.cz|accessdate=30 May 2017|language=cs}}</ref>
==Development== The game was announced on 16 May when Steam Greenlight campaign was launched.<ref name="Dark Train se vrací se samostatnou textovou adventurou Coupe - Games.cz"/><ref name="Introduction into Dark Train: Coupe news">{{cite web|title=Introduction into Dark Train: Coupe news|url=http://www.moddb.com/games/dark-train-coupe/news/introduction-into-dark-train-coupe|website=Mod DB|accessdate=30 May 2017|language=en}}</ref>
==Gameplay== The game is opposite to the original Dark Train. While Dark Train was a nontextual adventure game, DarkTrain: Coupe is a visual novel told through dialogues and text. Player is sometimes given opportunity to make a decision that will influence game's progress and eventually the ending. The game itself is non-linear.<ref name="Na unikátní českou vyřezávanou hru Dark Train naváže vizuální román">{{cite web|title=Na unikátní českou vyřezávanou hru Dark Train naváže vizuální román|url=http://bonusweb.idnes.cz/dark-train-coupe-02n-/Novinky.aspx?c=A170529_154420_bw-novinky_oz|website=iDNES.cz|accessdate=30 May 2017|date=30 May 2017}}</ref><ref name="Česká hra Dark Train: Coupe sa hlási o pozornosť CzechGamer">{{cite web|title=Česká hra Dark Train: Coupe sa hlási o pozornosť|url=http://www.czechgamer.com/27012/ceska-hra-dark-train-coupe-sa-hlasi-o-pozornos.html|website=www.czechgamer.com|accessdate=30 May 2017|language=cs}}</ref><ref name="Dark Train: Coupe prepares to embark this summer">{{cite web|title=Dark Train: Coupe prepares to embark this summer|url=https://adventuregamers.com/news/view/32831|website=Adventure Gamers|accessdate=30 May 2017}}</ref> Whole gameplay is supposed to be textual.<ref name="Introduction into Dark Train: Coupe news"/>
==Story== The main character is Ann Tagrezbung before she became mechanical squid from original [[Dark Train]] and still was a human. Whole game is set in Border City.<ref name="České štúdio Paperash oznamuje prequel k Dark Train s podtitulom Coupe">{{cite web|last1=s.r.o.|first1=Sector|title=České štúdio Paperash oznamuje prequel k Dark Train s podtitulom Coupe|url=http://www.sector.sk/novinka/135405/ceske-studio-paperash-oznamuje-prequel-k-dark-train-s-podtitulom-coupe.htm|website=Sector.sk|accessdate=30 May 2017}}</ref><ref name="Przygodowo logiczny Dark Train: Coupe trafił na Steam Greenlight - newsy z lubiegrac.pl">{{cite web|title=Przygodowo logiczny Dark Train: Coupe trafił na Steam Greenlight - newsy z lubiegrac.pl|url=https://lubiegrac.pl/news,przygodowo-logiczny-dark-train-coupe-trafil-na-steam-greenlight|website=lubiegrac.pl|accessdate=30 May 2017|language=pl}}</ref>
