ts and Memorials on Waymarking.com|website=waymarking.com|accessdate=September 7, 2017}}</ref> *Philadelphia, Pennsylvania, [[Cradle of Liberty Council]] (1937) *Pittsburgh, Pennsylvania (1937) *[[The Scout (Portland, Oregon)|Portland, Oregon]] (1972)<ref name="flickr">{{cite web|url=https://www.flickr.com/photos/atul666/sets/72157622228706232/|title=The Scout|website=Flickr|accessdate=September 7, 2017}}</ref><ref name="blogspot">{{cite web|url=http://cyclotram.blogspot.com/2009/09/ideal-scout.html|website=cyclotram.blogspot.com|title=cyclotram: The Ideal Scout|accessdate=September 7, 2017}}</ref> *Raleigh, North Carolina *Reedesville, Pennsylvania (1992) *Sharpsburg, Pennsylvania (1937) *Sioux Falls, South Dakota<ref name="waymarking5">{{cite web|url=http://www.waymarking.com/waymarks/WMBT9C_The_Ideal_Scout_Statue_Sioux_Falls_SD|title="The Ideal Scout" Statue – Sioux Falls, SD - Scouts Monuments and Memorials on Waymarking.com|website=waymarking.com|accessdate=September 7, 2017}}</ref> *St. Paul, Minnesota (1965) *University of Pennsylvania (1937) *Westlake, Texas, Scouting U, Westlake Campus (Center for Professional Development) Eric Hansen Park, Kenai, Alaska
