'''''The Music Lesson''''' (French: '''La lecon de musique''') is a 1917 [[oil painting]] by [[Henri Matisse]].<ref name="flam">Flam, Jack D. (2006). Matisse in transition:
around Laurette. Norton Museum of Art</ref> 

It is currently on display at the Barnes Foundation in Philadelphia, Pennsylvania. The painting is 96 3/8 x 79 in. (244.7 x 200.7&nbsp;cm).

